headline: Quarterra Announces Start of Leasing at Tavin Apartments
summary: Quarterra Multifamily, a subsidiary of Lennar Corporation and a vertically integrated multifamily apartment builder, developer, and asset manager, today announced the start of leasing at Tavin, a modern multifamily community in Seattle's Crown Hill neighborhood. Developed with investment partner CPPIB, Tavin brings contemporary living to one of Seattle's most distinctive neighborhoods.
